<h1 class="hero-h">Cost to start a gym <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">in 2026.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">A definitive, line-item breakdown of what it actually costs to open a gym in 2026. Real numbers across facility, equipment, licensing, software, staff, marketing, and working capital, by gym format (boutique, CrossFit, personal training studio, full-service). Built from operator observation, vendor pricing, and current market data. Use the companion calculator to estimate your specific situation.</p>
</div></div>

